      public static List<Map<String,​Object>> getNodeList​(@NonNull @NonNull Map<String,​Object> content, @NonNull @NonNull Key contentKey)

      Because it's impossible to avoid warnings when casting with generics, we specify SuppressWarnings with "unchecked" to this getNodeList(Map, Key) method.
